173 A.3d 601 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. LAZARO R. GUITEREZ, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-323 September Term 2017

079847 November 14, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000801-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

*186It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
